<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate.ejs") %>
    <style>
        .policy-container {
            max-width: 760px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 80px 24px 120px;
        }
        
        .policy-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #222222;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.25;
        }
        
        .policy-subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #717171;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .policy-section {
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }
        
        .policy-section h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #222222;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        
        .policy-section h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #222222;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        
        .policy-section p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #222222;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .policy-section ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .policy-section li {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #222222;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .contact-section {
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 32px;
            margin-top: 64px;
        }
        
        .contact-section h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        .breadcrumb {
            background: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .breadcrumb-item + .breadcrumb-item::before {
            content: ">";
            color: #717171;
        }
        
        .breadcrumb-item a {
            color: #222222;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .breadcrumb-item a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .breadcrumb-item.active {
            color: #717171;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">

        <main>
            <div class="policy-container">
                
                <h1 class="policy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="policy-subtitle">Last updated: September 3, 2025</p>
                
                <div class="policy-section">
                    <h2>Welcome to WanderLust</h2>
                    <p>WanderLust respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our services.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="policy-section">
                    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
                    <h3>Information you give us</h3>
                    <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Create an account and complete your profile</li>
                        <li>Make or receive a booking request</li>
                        <li>Contact us for customer support</li>
                        <li>Fill out surveys or participate in promotions</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h3>Information we automatically collect</h3>
                    <p>When you use our platform, we automatically collect certain information, including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Usage information and log data</li>
                        <li>Device information</li>
                        <li>Location information</li>
                        <li>Cookies and similar technologies</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="policy-section">
                    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
                        <li>Process transactions and send related information</li>
                        <li>Send you technical notices and support messages</li>
                        <li>Communicate with you about products, services, and events</li>
                        <li>Monitor and analyze trends and usage</li>
                        <li>Detect, prevent, and address technical issues and security</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="policy-section">
                    <h2>Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
                    <p>We may share information about you in the following circumstances:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>With your consent:</strong> We may share your information with third parties when you give us consent to do so</li>
                        <li><strong>For legal reasons:</strong> We may share your information if required by law or in response to legal process</li>
                        <li><strong>Business transfers:</strong> Information may be transferred in connection with mergers or acquisitions</li>
                        <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> We work with third-party service providers who need access to your information</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="policy-section">
                    <h2>Data Security</h2>
                    <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information from loss, theft, misuse, unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction. However, no internet or electronic storage system is 100% secure.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="policy-section">
                    <h2>Your Rights and Choices</h2>
                    <p>Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information, including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access and portability</li>
                        <li>Rectification and erasure</li>
                        <li>Restriction and objection</li>
                        <li>Automated decision-making</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-section">
                    <h3>Questions or Concerns?</h3>
                    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at:</p>
                    <p><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@wanderlust.com<br>
                    <strong>Address:</strong> WanderLust Privacy Team, 123 Travel Street, Adventure City, AC 12345</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

    </div>